
///Lesson No..1
// Coding part of .............

#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    cout << "Hello, World!" << endl;
    return 0;
}



// explanation ..................
1..#include <iostream> →  this allows input/output functionality in our code.
2..main() → entry point of every C++ program this is starting point of prpgram.
3..cout → prints output to the console.
4..endl → ends the line.
5.. int-> Int define type of data in this section int means "Integer".
